race.description: Pfd Food Services / Nella Contracting Maiden Plate
race.comment: THE BULLET (6) finds the maiden win elusive but looks close to breaking the duck after being beaten a lip in his last two. The mile looks perfect for him and he's drawn to advantage. Better chance than any. CODONAS (3) has only been sound in his two runs back. Strips fitter third-up and will appreciate the rise to the mile. Boudvillain's booking adds confidence he can run well. LA CHAPARRON (10) was well below her best last time at Dubbo but her prior form stacks right up. Drawn to advantage for Gallagher. Can give this a big shake. DEEPFIELD KING (4) was less effective last time at Gilgandra but did have some excuses. Can get things back on track and is worth including.
